<l>uṟṟavaṉ ṟīrppāṉ maruntuḻaic celvāṉeṉ</l>
<l>ṟappāṉāṟ kūṟṟē maruntu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Medical science consists of four parts, viz., patient, physician, medicine and compounder; and each of these (again) contains four sub-divisions.</l>
